claim: Jeffrey Dahmer was a sex offender from Milwaukee.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Jeffrey Lionel Dahmer  (  May 21 , 1960 -- November 28 , 1994  )  , also known as the Milwaukee Cannibal , was an American serial killer and sex offender , who committed the rape , murder , and dismemberment of seventeen men and boys between 1978 and 1991 .
